<p class="MsoNormal">Access the File Server or Directory:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Log in to the file server or the system responsible for managing the shared drives.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>Open the <strong>Shared Folder</strong> where the user will be added.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Open Permissions Settings:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Right-click on the shared drive/folder.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Select <strong>Properties</strong>, then go to the <strong>Security</strong> or <strong>Sharing</strong> tab depending on the system</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Add the User:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Click <strong>Add</strong> to open the user/group selection dialog.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Search for the user's name or username in the organization&rsquo;s directory.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Select the user and click <strong>OK</strong>.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Assign Permissions:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Once the user is added, define their level of access:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Read</strong>: The user can only view the contents of the drive.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Write/Modify</strong>: The user can view and edit files.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong>Full Control</strong>: The user can add, modify, and delete files, as well as change permissions.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Assign the appropriate permissions as per the request.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Apply and Save:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Click <strong>Apply</strong> and then <strong>OK</strong> to save the settings.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo5;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ensure the changes have been propagated to all subfolders if necessary.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Notify the User:</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo6;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Inform the user and their manager that they have been granted access to the shared drive.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Procedure for Deleting a User from S/H Drives:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Access the File Server or Directory</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l9 level1 lfo7; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Log in to the file server or network system managing the shared drive.</span></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l9 level1 lfo7; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Navigate to the shared folder from which the user should be removed.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Open Permissions Settings:</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l11 level1 lfo8; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Right-click the shared drive or folder.</span></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l11 level1 lfo8; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Select <strong>Properties</strong>, and go to the <strong>Security</strong> or <strong>Sharing</strong> tab.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Remove the User:</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l6 level1 lfo9; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">In the <strong>Group or Usernames</strong> section, find the user to be removed.</span></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l6 level1 lfo9; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Highlight the user and click <strong>Remove</strong>.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Apply and Save:</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l7 level1 lfo10; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Click <strong>Apply</strong> and <strong>OK</strong> to save changes.</span></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l7 level1 lfo10; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Ensure all inherited permissions are adjusted, so the user cannot access subfolders.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Verify the Removal:</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l10 level1 lfo11; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Confirm that the user no longer has access to the shared drive.</span></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l10 level1 lfo11; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Use administrative tools to verify user permissions or request confirmation from the user&rsquo;s department.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Notify Relevant Stakeholders:</span></strong></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-list: l4 level1 lfo12; tab-stops: list .5in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">Inform the user and their manager (if required) about the access removal.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in;"><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 115%;">&nbsp;</span></p>